<div class="lp-wrap">
  <section>
    <div class="lp-hero">
      <div>
        <div class="lp-kicker">Modern Library Experience</div>
        <h1>Your catalog,<br><em>beautifully</em> organized.</h1>
        <p>Discover titles, manage inventory, and keep every book in its place — in a clean workspace built for bookstores and their teams.</p>
        <div class="lp-actions">
          <%= link_to books_path, class: "lp-btn-main" do %>
            &#9783; Browse Collection
          <% end %>
          <%= link_to new_book_path, class: "lp-btn-ghost" do %>
            + Add a Book
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-stats">
          <div class="lp-stat"><strong>REST API</strong><small>Fully connected</small></div>
          <div class="lp-stat"><strong>Fast</strong><small>Sub-100ms queries</small></div>
          <div class="lp-stat"><strong>Clean UI</strong><small>Zero clutter</small></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-panel">
        <p class="lp-panel-label">Everything in one place</p>
        <ul class="lp-checklist">
          <li><span class="lp-dot"><svg viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><polyline points="2,5 4.5,7.5 8,3" stroke="#1a3d2b" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span>Maintain a neat digital shelf with rich metadata — title, author, pricing, and more.</span></li>
          <li><span class="lp-dot"><svg viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><polyline points="2,5 4.5,7.5 8,3" stroke="#1a3d2b" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span>Update inventory and pricing in seconds, without digging through menus.</span></li>
          <li><span class="lp-dot"><svg viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><polyline points="2,5 4.5,7.5 8,3" stroke="#1a3d2b" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span>Connect external tools via a clean, documented REST API.</span></li>
          <li><span class="lp-dot"><svg viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><polyline points="2,5 4.5,7.5 8,3" stroke="#1a3d2b" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span>Monitor library health, background jobs, and performance in real time.</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="lp-section-divider"></div>

  <section>
    <div class="lp-features">
      <span class="lp-sec-kicker">Capabilities</span>
      <h2>Everything your team needs</h2>
      <div class="lp-card-grid">
        <div class="lp-card">
          <div class="lp-icon-wrap lp-icon-wrap--green">&#128218;</div>
          <h3>Extensive Library</h3>
          <p>Search, browse, and organize your entire catalog in a polished, readable interface.</p>
          <%= link_to books_path, class: "lp-card-link" do %>
            View Books &rarr;
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-card">
          <div class="lp-icon-wrap lp-icon-wrap--sage">&#123;&#125;</div>
          <h3>Developer API</h3>
          <p>Integrate your tools with the BookStore API for automation and custom workflows.</p>
          <%= link_to new_book_path, class: "lp-card-link" do %>
            API Docs &rarr;
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-card">
          <div class="lp-icon-wrap lp-icon-wrap--amber">&#9741;</div>
          <h3>System Dashboard</h3>
          <p>Track library health, background jobs, and key performance metrics at a glance.</p>
          <%= link_to dashboard_path, class: "lp-card-link" do %>
            Open Dashboard &rarr;
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>